{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "story_aprl_set_1", "eventName": "獵人的視線", "entryType": "NONE", "storyCode": null, "avgTag": "幕間", "storyName": "獵人的視線", "storyInfo": "獵人時期的四月遇到強盜搶劫，困住對方並得知其感染者身份後，有所觸動的她選擇了合作。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_barracks"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$drift_intro", "key": "$drift_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_365_aprl_1#1$1", "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_transmissionget"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.7}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喂，是我，愛爾莉。", "name": "愛爾莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#1$1"}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "剛剛營地的廣播你聽到了嗎？......對喔，我現在還在任務中，離鋼鐵蘿蔔城大概也就走個一天一夜的距離吧。", "name": "愛爾莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#1$1"}, {"id": 15, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_365_aprl_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是啊！本來我以為這兩天就可以回家了，結果今天接到新的通知，我們這支勘察隊在中轉站補給之後，還要去更遠的礦區。", "name": "愛爾莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#3$1"}, {"id": 17, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_365_aprl_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，公司的隊伍說走就走，安排我當護衛，我也沒有什麼辦法呢。", "name": "愛爾莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#1$1"}, {"id": 19, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_365_aprl_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以，這周的聚會我去不了啦，不好意思哦。", "name": "愛爾莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#1$1"}, {"id": 21, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_365_aprl_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......當然會覺得有點可惜啦，畢竟大家準備了這麼久嘛。好不容易找到那間廢棄的礦石倉庫可以做場地，又花了那麼大力氣把它佈置好。", "name": "愛爾莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#3$1"}, {"id": 23, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_365_aprl_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，這樣一看，還好我負責的工作前期就完成了呢，現在突然到不了場也不會誤什麼事。", "name": "愛爾莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#7$1"}, {"id": 25, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_365_aprl_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（難過）嗯，是哦，反正以後還有很多機會......", "name": "愛爾莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#6$1"}, {"id": 27, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_365_aprl_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......下一次聚會的時候，天氣應該就很暖和了呢，之前我們一起逛街的時候買的那條連衣裙總算可以穿了。", "name": "愛爾莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#3$1"}, {"id": 29, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_365_aprl_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......對吧，你也很期待吧？我還買了能搭配的耳飾呢。", "name": "愛爾莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#7$1"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_365_aprl_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，對了，你們之前說排練了一首我喜歡的歌要在聚會上表演，但是要給我個驚喜，所以先不告訴我是哪首......現在總可以說了吧？", "name": "愛爾莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#1$1"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_365_aprl_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我猜不到啦，我喜歡的樂隊兩隻手都數不過來，每支樂隊還有那麼多好專輯，要我從中挑一首歌也太難了吧。", "name": "愛爾莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#3$1"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也不要再等下一次聚會啦，萬一下次我又被公司安排長期任務了呢？", "name": "愛爾莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#3$1"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_365_aprl_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......喔，那首啊，確實很應景呢！", "name": "愛爾莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#1$1"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_365_aprl_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們可要成為超級明星組合喔，那樣我就可以實現在家門口看演唱會的心願了。", "name": "愛爾莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#3$1"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_365_aprl_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "愛爾莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#6$1"}, {"id": 42, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不著痕跡地，卡特斯女孩突然用手捂住了通訊器的收音位置。"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......哇，那個花枝招展的小卡特斯？不會吧，她怎麼在這，最近還有人敢委託任務給她？", "name": "獵人的聲音"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但她依然是註冊獵人，原則上她是可以在營地停留的，雖然是獨來獨往......", "name": "工作人員的聲音"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_365_aprl_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......啊，隊伍要出發了呢，本來我還想跟你抱怨一下這次任務有多麻煩，看來只能下次再說啦。", "name": "愛爾莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#3$1"}, {"id": 49, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，我回到城裡再聯繫你們。", "name": "愛爾莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#3$1"}, {"id": 50, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$transmission", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果我是她的話，我就會識相地低下頭趕快走掉。不過看她穿得那麼惹眼，大概還是和以前一樣不知好歹吧，哈哈哈......", "name": "獵人的聲音"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_365_aprl_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......啊，趕路的時候就把耳機戴上吧。", "name": "愛爾莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#6$1"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_365_aprl_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，清淨多啦！為了不會這麼想睡，路上就聽點動感的音樂吧！", "name": "愛爾莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#3$1"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_forest", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness01_intro", "key": "$darkness01_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_365_aprl_1#6$1", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咦，最近的價目表被我放在哪裡了......啊，對，這裡寫了裂獸的價格最高。", "name": "愛爾莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#6$1"}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過我也不會處理那種龐然大物呀......還是算了。", "name": "愛爾莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#6$1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "以前只要把野獸趕走就好了，現在卻要主動去樹林裡找它們的麻煩呢。", "name": "愛爾莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#6$1"}, {"id": 78, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_365_aprl_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還好只差一點點就存夠目標金額了，就算再捕幾隻羽獸，應該也夠了吧。", "name": "愛爾莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#1$1"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_365_aprl_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "按照公司福利政策，存下來的錢差不多能買一台公司淘汰的舊投影儀了呢，那樣就可以躺在床上看買來的影碟了。", "name": "愛爾莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#3$1"}, {"id": 82, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_365_aprl_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不不，有錢的話，首先還是改善一下住宿條件吧。如果換間隔音好一點的出租屋，半夜出完任務回家或者搬動傢俱就不會吵到鄰居了。", "name": "愛爾莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#2$1"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_365_aprl_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，我還是不太擅長做長線計畫呢......", "name": "愛爾莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#1$1"}, {"id": 86, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$leaveshake", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "xstrength": 3.0, "ystrength": 3.0, "vibrato": 20.0, "randomness": 70.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_365_aprl_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......有動靜了。", "name": "愛爾莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#6$1"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不知道今天的運氣怎麼樣呢......受傷的野獸總是會跑掉，從書上學來的陷阱也不知道好不好用。", "name": "愛爾莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#6$1"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_008", "blackstart": 0.4, "blackend": 0.6, "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.8}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_365_aprl_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是人啊！好險好險——", "name": "愛爾莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#2$1"}, {"id": 103, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_arrowshot"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "middle", "type": "move", "xpos": 200.0, "fadetime": 0.3, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喂，你好——別認錯啦，我不是獵物，我是獵人呀！我都穿得這麼鮮豔了，應該不像野獸吧？", "name": "愛爾莉"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$chasing_intro", "key": "$chasing_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_008", "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們可沒認錯，你就是我們的獵物。", "name": "強盜頭目"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_008"}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "值錢的東西都交出來，不然別怪我們不客氣。", "name": "強盜頭目"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_008"}, {"id": 117, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_007", "name2": "avg_npc_007", "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_365_aprl_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "欸，好像真的有其他人靠過來了......", "name": "愛爾莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#2$1"}, {"id": 124, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "躲在那邊樹上的，我背後石頭旁邊的......", "name": "愛爾莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#2$1"}, {"id": 125, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "middle", "type": "move", "fadetime": 0.3, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_arrowshot"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_007"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我倒數三次，乖乖把錢拿來。否則，就不是一支箭這麼簡單的事情了。", "name": "強盜頭目"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_007"}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "三。", "name": "強盜頭目"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_007"}, {"id": 134, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_365_aprl_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......不行哦。", "name": "愛爾莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#5$1"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_007"}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "二。", "name": "強盜頭目"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_007"}, {"id": 138, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_365_aprl_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這些錢可是我好不容易存下來的。", "name": "愛爾莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#5$1"}, {"id": 140, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_007"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一。", "name": "強盜頭目"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_007"}, {"id": 142, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_365_aprl_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要不你們還是試試看能不能追上我吧！", "name": "愛爾莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#5$1"}, {"id": 144, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$drift_intro", "key": "$drift_loop", "volume": 0.2}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_barracks", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "amount": 0.8, "keep": "true"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_365_aprl_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_365_aprl_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦，愛爾莉，你又過來啦。", "name": "雜貨市場老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#1$1"}, {"id": 157, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_365_aprl_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是呀，今天總算把家裡收拾完啦。沒想到我的房間不大，雜七雜八的東西還挺多的呢。", "name": "愛爾莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#1$1"}, {"id": 159, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_365_aprl_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我來看看......哎呀，這種可拆卸式的收納櫃，二手貨不太容易賣出去的哦？而且上面還有膠帶留下的痕跡。", "name": "雜貨市場老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#1$1"}, {"id": 161, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_365_aprl_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，那是我之前在櫃子側面貼了可以當等身鏡用的鏡面貼紙，後來有天心情不好，就把它撕掉了。", "name": "愛爾莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#3$1"}, {"id": 163, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_365_aprl_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好像是不太美觀呢......那您就估價低一點吧。", "name": "愛爾莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#1$1"}, {"id": 165, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_365_aprl_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咦，這件衣服還是全新的，你要當二手貨賣掉嗎？是不是有點太可惜了？", "name": "雜貨市場老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#1$1"}, {"id": 167, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_365_aprl_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我也有點惋惜呢......不過這件衣服的款式不太合適，會露出後背，所以沒辦法啦。", "name": "愛爾莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#1$1"}, {"id": 169, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_365_aprl_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你的礦石病，石頭是長在後背上？", "name": "雜貨市場老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#1$1"}, {"id": 171, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_365_aprl_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯......", "name": "愛爾莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#6$1"}, {"id": 173, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_365_aprl_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，我明白的。愛爾莉，你剛搬過來沒多久吧？", "name": "雜貨市場老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#6$1"}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我看你連續好幾天跑到這邊來賣東西了，是遇到什麼緊急情況了嗎？", "name": "雜貨市場老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#6$1"}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡都是感染者，有些話我們悄悄說，沒關係的。", "name": "雜貨市場老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#6$1"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_365_aprl_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......我沒事，老闆。我只是在這裡一直找不到工作，所以想換個地方試試。", "name": "愛爾莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#7$1"}, {"id": 179, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_365_aprl_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這些東西反正也帶不走，乾脆就賣掉好啦。", "name": "愛爾莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#3$1"}, {"id": 181, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_365_aprl_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，說是換個地方，別的地方就能好過嗎？你想好去哪裡了嗎？", "name": "雜貨市場老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#3$1"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_365_aprl_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯......在廣告上看到了一家公司，雖然有點遠，但我覺得可以去試一試。", "name": "愛爾莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#1$1"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_365_aprl_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我已經為新城市的生活存好一筆錢啦，接下來只要手裡的錢夠買長途車票就好啦。", "name": "愛爾莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#7$1"}, {"id": 187, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_365_aprl_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "放心吧，之前我認真計畫了一下，手頭還是挺寬裕的呢。", "name": "愛爾莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#3$1"}, {"id": 189, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_365_aprl_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且就算現在沒有工作，我還有這把弓呢。運氣好的時候能在城市周邊捕到一些野獸，營地也會有收購皮毛和獸肉的商人。", "name": "愛爾莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#7$1"}, {"id": 191, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "運氣差一點的話......應該也不會餓死吧。", "name": "愛爾莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#7$1"}, {"id": 192, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_365_aprl_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哎，你年紀輕輕的，打獵時可千萬小心，遇到源石晶簇一定要繞著走......別讓病情惡化得太快啊。", "name": "雜貨市場老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#7$1"}, {"id": 194, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_365_aprl_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哎呀，我都跟著採礦車隊這麼多年了，怎麼會不知道這些呢？", "name": "愛爾莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#1$1"}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過原本想著存下來一點錢的話先買個二手音箱或者投影儀什麼的，沒想到第一次手頭有錢會是這個感覺的啊......", "name": "愛爾莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#1$1"}, {"id": 197, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_365_aprl_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不對，東西都賣光了，好像不能說是變得有錢了。", "name": "愛爾莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#3$1"}, {"id": 199, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_365_aprl_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既然這麼多東西都拖出來賣掉了，那你應該馬上就要離開了吧？", "name": "雜貨市場老闆"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#3$1"}, {"id": 201, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_365_aprl_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，明天早上就出發啦。", "name": "愛爾莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#1$1"}, {"id": 203, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 0.0, "amount": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_forest", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$chasing_intro", "key": "$chasing_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "middle", "type": "move", "xpos": 200.0, "fadetime": 0.3, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "middle", "type": "move", "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_365_aprl_1#5$1", "fadetime": 0.7}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃，你們兩個拿刀的傢伙跑得真快啊......！", "name": "愛爾莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#5$1"}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是我的行李包交出去的話，我就真的什麼都沒有了......感覺那樣也很難活下去呢，還是算了吧。", "name": "愛爾莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#5$1"}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "果然還是運氣不太好啊，要不是買長途車票差一點點錢，又不想動用封存好的那筆生活費的話，本來不用再打獵的。", "name": "愛爾莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#5$1"}, {"id": 223, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喂，我說得這麼大聲，你們應該也聽得到吧？我還以為你們會同情一下我呢。", "name": "愛爾莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#5$1"}, {"id": 224, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "middle", "type": "jump", "ypos": 100.0, "times": 1.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_clothmovement"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.6}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在幾乎被強盜手中的刀刃觸及的瞬間，靈活的卡特斯猛然躍起，攀上一根樹枝。"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "middle", "type": "move", "xpos": 200.0, "fadetime": 0.3, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "middle", "type": "move", "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_007", "fadetime": 0.7}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$bodyfalldown1", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 0.7}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_365_aprl_1#1$1", "fadetime": 0.7}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，看來陷阱是有用的呢，而且連那邊的弩手都踩到機關掉進捕獸網了。", "name": "愛爾莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#1$1"}, {"id": 246, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你——！", "name": "強盜頭目"}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_365_aprl_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我沒有想過要跟人戰鬥啦，不過現在你們落進了陷阱，就算是獵物了。", "name": "愛爾莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#5$1"}, {"id": 250, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我雖然年紀不大，但很早就開始接受獵人的職業訓練了哦，對於自己的弓箭，還有引誘獵物的手段，我還是很自信的。", "name": "愛爾莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#5$1"}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然後，因為陷阱是用來對付野獸的嘛，所以掙扎得越用力，越容易受傷哦。", "name": "愛爾莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#5$1"}, {"id": 252, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_365_aprl_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（這樣的威脅應該夠了吧？電視劇裡好像都是這麼演的。）", "name": "愛爾莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#6$1"}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（唉，不知道附近有沒有治安隊，或者哪家公司的專業安保人員，等會去營地求助試試看吧。）", "name": "愛爾莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#6$1"}, {"id": 255, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_365_aprl_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 257, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呼......現在我們應該可以悠閒地聊天了吧。", "name": "愛爾莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#5$1"}, {"id": 258, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 259, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你......你要做什麼？先把弓放下來，我們有話好好說。", "name": "強盜頭目"}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_365_aprl_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 261, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我只是確認一下陷阱夠不夠可靠，沒什麼問題的話，我就要回營地找人把你們帶走啦。", "name": "愛爾莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#5$1"}, {"id": 262, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，不行，求你......我們會死的。", "name": "猶豫的強盜"}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_365_aprl_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "欸，這麼怕被抓，難道你們已經搶過很多人了？", "name": "愛爾莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#2$1"}, {"id": 266, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒有，只是......", "name": "猶豫的強盜"}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們是得了病的人。是感染者。", "name": "強盜頭目"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這一點就夠了，獵人。你說自己不跟人戰鬥，但你不會同情牲畜，對吧？", "name": "強盜頭目"}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_365_aprl_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "愛爾莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#6$1"}, {"id": 272, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "與其花時間給感染者定罪，不如直接......", "name": "強盜頭目"}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_365_aprl_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "夠了。", "name": "愛爾莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#5$1"}, {"id": 276, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_365_aprl_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我......", "name": "愛爾莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#6$1"}, {"id": 278, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 280, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 281, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_barracks", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$drift_intro", "key": "$drift_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "amount": 0.8, "keep": "true"}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果在以前，我還會說那傢伙毫無獵人的素養，但是現在她是感染者了，那可不能再把她跟我們放在一起比較了，哈哈哈！", "name": "獵人的聲音"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是不是註冊獵人有什麼關係，現在還有誰找她做事嗎？", "name": "獵人的聲音"}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 0.0, "amount": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_forest", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_365_aprl_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你們為什麼會來當強盜？", "name": "愛爾莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#6$1"}, {"id": 298, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這有什麼好問的？感染了礦石病，工作丟了，但總得想辦法活下去。", "name": "強盜頭目"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "和大部分感染者一樣，我們兄弟三個之前也是礦工，都幹得挺久了。", "name": "強盜頭目"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_365_aprl_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那......公司的保障措施呢？", "name": "愛爾莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#5$1"}, {"id": 303, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是說感染者補償金？被我們那個礦井負責人私吞了吧。我沒聽說有哪個一起幹活的人感染後收到過自己的補償金。", "name": "強盜頭目"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看你穿得這麼光鮮，難道是什麼沒見過感染者的有錢人家大小姐？如果你要找個地方施捨自己的同情心，我這裡悲慘故事多的是。", "name": "強盜頭目"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_365_aprl_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，我只是普通人，非常普通......", "name": "愛爾莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#6$1"}, {"id": 308, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_365_aprl_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，我倒是有個想法。既然你們知道是誰拿走了你們的補償金，為什麼不找他本人拿回來呢？", "name": "愛爾莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#1$1"}, {"id": 310, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_offce", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkness01_intro", "key": "$darkness01_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$doorknockquite", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "請進。", "name": "礦井負責人"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_365_aprl_1#1$1", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您好，我是這次被安排來臨時執行護送任務的獵人，這是我的註冊獵人證明，然後這是臨時委任文件。", "name": "愛爾莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#1$1"}, {"id": 329, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯？我不記得見過你，而且我們的獵人......", "name": "礦井負責人"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_365_aprl_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "另外，我還有三位同伴，會協助我完成任務哦。", "name": "愛爾莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#3$1"}, {"id": 333, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別胡鬧，哪有——", "name": "礦井負責人"}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_008", "name2": "avg_npc_007", "fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 3.0}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們......", "name": "礦井負責人"}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_008", "name2": "avg_npc_007", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們只是想要回我們的錢。", "name": "持刀的強盜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_007"}, {"id": 344, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_unsheathe"}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別、別把刀架在......救、救命......", "name": "礦井負責人"}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_008", "name2": "avg_npc_007", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不要想著呼救，我們被礦場拋棄之後，可是實打實地幹了好幾票搶劫，刀不會慢的。", "name": "強盜頭目"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_008"}, {"id": 351, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_forest", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "amount": 0.8, "keep": "true"}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_008", "name2": "avg_365_aprl_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_008", "name2": "avg_365_aprl_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......這樣真的能行？", "name": "強盜頭目"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_008"}, {"id": 362, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_008", "name2": "avg_365_aprl_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒問題。", "name": "愛爾莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#1$1"}, {"id": 364, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "總之，我先去營地打聽一下，尋找最近會前往那處礦場的獵人，大致瞭解一下任務情況。", "name": "愛爾莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#1$1"}, {"id": 365, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然後呢，如果對方是個好心人，願意幫助我們，那我們就頂替對方進入礦場。如果對方不願意幫忙，我們就提前以他的名義混進去。", "name": "愛爾莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#1$1"}, {"id": 366, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_008", "name2": "avg_365_aprl_1#3$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，我其實也不太會編謊話，到時候你們可能要幫我打圓場哦。", "name": "愛爾莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#3$1"}, {"id": 368, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_008", "name2": "avg_365_aprl_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從守衛那裡通過之後，路上只要避開所有人就好啦。", "name": "愛爾莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#1$1"}, {"id": 370, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_008", "name2": "avg_365_aprl_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說起來倒是容易。", "name": "強盜頭目"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_008"}, {"id": 372, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_008", "name2": "avg_365_aprl_1#7$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "畢竟我是獵人嘛，在不被發現這方面還是很有心得的，野獸的感官那麼靈敏，我都能躲過它們。", "name": "愛爾莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#7$1"}, {"id": 374, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_008", "name2": "avg_365_aprl_1#1$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要是被看到了，那就再想辦法嘛，我覺得我們長得也不是很可疑，陌生人就算看到了我們也不會記住吧。", "name": "愛爾莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#1$1"}, {"id": 376, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_008", "name2": "avg_365_aprl_1#1$1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘁，好吧，那我帶路。", "name": "強盜頭目"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_008"}, {"id": 378, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......獵人，你到底為什麼要幫我們？因為我們看起來太可憐了？", "name": "強盜頭目"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_008"}, {"id": 379, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_008", "name2": "avg_365_aprl_1#2$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 380, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，這倒沒有......", "name": "愛爾莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#2$1"}, {"id": 381, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_008", "name2": "avg_365_aprl_1#6$1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 382, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可能只是因為我有個問題想找人問問看。", "name": "愛爾莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#6$1"}, {"id": 383, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 384, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 386, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "CameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "fadetime": 0.0, "amount": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_offce", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 391, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_365_aprl_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，對了，關於你私吞感染者補償金這件事，我是不是還可以向公司舉報？", "name": "愛爾莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#3$1"}, {"id": 393, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "礦井負責人"}}, {"id": 395, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好，我給，我給就是了......全部給你們補上。", "name": "礦井負責人"}}, {"id": 396, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_008", "name2": "avg_npc_007", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 397, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不要承諾什麼支票之類的東西，我們只要實實在在的錢。", "name": "強盜頭目"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_008"}, {"id": 398, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果不是信任你，我們當初就會站在這裡等著你把錢拿出來。", "name": "強盜頭目"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_008"}, {"id": 399, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 400, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉......現金，那邊的保險箱......這是鑰匙。", "name": "礦井負責人"}}, {"id": 401, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_008", "name2": "avg_npc_007", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 402, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你去拿，就拿三人份的。", "name": "強盜頭目"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_008"}, {"id": 403, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_008", "name2": "avg_npc_007", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 404, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好......我們不能多拿一點嗎？", "name": "猶豫的強盜"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_007"}, {"id": 405, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_008", "name2": "avg_npc_007", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 406, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "以防萬一被查到。而且，在這傢伙面前我希望有尊嚴一些。", "name": "強盜頭目"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_008"}, {"id": 407, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 408, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "明明就是感染者，談什麼尊嚴......", "name": "礦井負責人"}}, {"id": 409, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那邊的獵人也夠奇怪的。我以為你也是來討要補償金的。", "name": "礦井負責人"}}, {"id": 410, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_365_aprl_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 411, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊......我只是想問一個問題。", "name": "愛爾莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#2$1"}, {"id": 412, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_365_aprl_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 413, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "既然你並不缺錢，為什麼要拿走感染者賴以生存的這筆補償金呢？", "name": "愛爾莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#5$1"}, {"id": 414, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 415, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......反正沒有後續就業機會，這筆錢遲早會被你們用光吧？把錢花在感染者身上，多浪費啊。", "name": "礦井負責人"}}, {"id": 416, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_008"}}, {"id": 417, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真讓人噁心。", "name": "強盜頭目"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_008"}, {"id": 418, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "獵人，你費這麼大勁就為了問這個問題？", "name": "強盜頭目"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_008"}, {"id": 419, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_365_aprl_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 420, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，也不是啦，只是之前我都沒想過這件事呢。", "name": "愛爾莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#2$1"}, {"id": 421, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_365_aprl_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 422, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......是誰奪走了公司給我的福利，又是為什麼？", "name": "愛爾莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#6$1"}, {"id": 423, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 424, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 425, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 426, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 427, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 428, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_barracks", "screenadapt": "showall"}}, {"id": 429, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 430, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$warm_intro", "key": "$warm_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 431, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 432, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 433, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_008"}}, {"id": 434, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，我們接下來想再回附近的城鎮碰碰運氣，也許還有用得著我們的工作。", "name": "強盜頭目"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_008"}, {"id": 435, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你真的不打算去找那些害了你的人算帳？", "name": "強盜頭目"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_008"}, {"id": 436, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_365_aprl_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 437, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔，好像沒辦法呢。因為一開始就沒注意是不是有人從中使壞，所以現在也完全不知道要去找誰問個清楚了。", "name": "愛爾莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#6$1"}, {"id": 438, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_365_aprl_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 439, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且我已經準備離開這裡啦，就把過去的事情全部拋下好了。", "name": "愛爾莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#7$1"}, {"id": 440, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_008"}}, {"id": 441, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對了，你之前說過在湊車票錢。", "name": "強盜頭目"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_008"}, {"id": 442, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你幫了我們這麼大的忙，還花了好幾天時間，我們替你把剩下的車票錢湊齊作為報答吧。", "name": "強盜頭目"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_008"}, {"id": 443, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖然也不是多大的數目......", "name": "強盜頭目"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_008"}, {"id": 444, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_365_aprl_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 445, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "欸，你們果然也是很好的人嘛。", "name": "愛爾莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#3$1"}, {"id": 446, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_008"}}, {"id": 447, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "說真的，沒想到你也是感染者，而且你跑到那個混帳東西面前，居然只是想問那麼簡單的問題。", "name": "強盜頭目"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_008"}, {"id": 448, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聽到那種話，你難道就滿意了嗎？", "name": "強盜頭目"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_008"}, {"id": 449, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_365_aprl_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 450, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然不滿意啦，他說的話我一點也不喜歡。", "name": "愛爾莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#6$1"}, {"id": 451, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是很多人都是那樣想的吧？其實根本不需要什麼理由，只是不用把感染者當回事而已。", "name": "愛爾莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#6$1"}, {"id": 452, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就連我自己也......", "name": "愛爾莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#6$1"}, {"id": 453, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 454, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_transmissionget"}}, {"id": 455, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 456, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_365_aprl_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 457, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咦......", "name": "愛爾莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#2$1"}, {"id": 458, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 459, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 460, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哇，愛爾莉，你居然接了！", "name": "通訊器那端的聲音"}}, {"id": 461, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們只是想呼叫你試試，沒想到你居然真的在信號區內。", "name": "通訊器那端的聲音"}}, {"id": 462, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼樣，能聽到嗎？這邊在演奏《四月》哦！雖然他們演奏得亂七八糟的，但勉強還能聽出來是什麼，對吧？", "name": "通訊器那端的聲音"}}, {"id": 463, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘿嘿，這樣你也算是沒錯過了！送給我們的愛爾莉，感謝你為鋼鐵蘿蔔城最偉大的藝術街區打下第一塊基石！", "name": "通訊器那端的聲音"}}, {"id": 464, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_365_aprl_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 465, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈哈哈......咳、咳咳......", "name": "愛爾莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#3$1"}, {"id": 466, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_365_aprl_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 467, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "愛爾莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#7$1"}, {"id": 468, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 469, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.5}}, {"id": 470, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 471, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "愛爾莉，如果你要親口跟他們道別，這就是最後的機會了。"}}, {"id": 472, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果你想問問你的朋友們接不接受一個感染者，這也是最好的機會了，趁著你還沒有遠走高飛，你們的關係還很熱絡。"}}, {"id": 473, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——這樣想著的卡特斯，只是安靜地握著通訊器聽完了整首歌。"}}, {"id": 474, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 475, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_365_aprl_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 476, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......替我轉達一下，我覺得如果他們多多練習，音樂還是可以變得好聽的！", "name": "愛爾莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#4$1"}, {"id": 477, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_365_aprl_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 478, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好啦，就這樣吧。你們一定要玩得開心哦。", "name": "愛爾莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#3$1"}, {"id": 479, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 480, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$transmission"}}, {"id": 481, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 482, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_365_aprl_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 483, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，那幾個感染者已經走掉了。", "name": "愛爾莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#2$1"}, {"id": 484, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_365_aprl_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 485, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......如果之後有機會的話，我再寫信把我的事情告訴朋友們吧。", "name": "愛爾莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#1$1"}, {"id": 486, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_365_aprl_1#7$1"}}, {"id": 487, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "畢竟成為感染者之後，我就沒怎麼感受過這樣的熱情和善意了......我還是想讓他們再多陪陪我呀。", "name": "愛爾莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#7$1"}, {"id": 488, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_365_aprl_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 489, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是說到底，比起別人的看法，最重要的還是......我自己怎麼想。", "name": "愛爾莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#1$1"}, {"id": 490, "prop": "character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_365_aprl_1#3$1"}}, {"id": 491, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......好啦，該出發了。希望那家公司的廣告不是虛假宣傳呢。", "name": "愛爾莉"}, "figure_art": "avg_365_aprl_1#3$1"}, {"id": 492, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 493, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 494, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 495, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 496, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 497, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 498, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}